PO FRANCUSKU:
Rozumie pani?

00:47:50.119 --> 00:47:52.119 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Proszę bardzo.

00:47:56.320 --> 00:47:58.559 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Drogie panie, uwaga.

00:48:03.559 --> 00:48:05.960 line:85% position:50% size:80%
ENERGICZNA MUZYKA

00:48:06.039 --> 00:48:19.800 line:85% position:50% size:80%
♪

00:48:19.880 --> 00:48:21.880 line:85% position:50% size:80%
O, no!

00:48:21.960 --> 00:48:26.039 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
Drogie panie, to jest Haydn,
tak nie można, proszę bardzo!

00:48:31.400 --> 00:48:33.400 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Proszę, początek.

00:48:35.639 --> 00:48:37.639 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Przepraszam.

00:48:38.239 --> 00:48:40.239 line:85% position:50% size:80%
SPOKOJNA MELODIA

00:48:45.400 --> 00:48:47.400 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Jeszcze raz.

